title: National Hockey League - Canadian Players' Hometowns, Canada,
name: National Hockey League - Canadian Players' Hometowns, Canada,
description: Canada is a hockey nation. Looking at the birthplaces of active NHL players, it seems the talent is spread across the country. Other information in this dataset includes players' heights, weights, and birth dates. This data was compiled from active rosters found at www.nhl.com, accessed on 8.13.07. Latitudes and longitudes were assigned to each city of birth, so once mapped, each point represents a player's birthplace.
